library(conflicted)
library(tidyverse)
library(treemapify)
library(gapminder)

# gapminder2007
df <- gapminder |>
  dplyr::filter(year == 2007)

df |>
  ggplot(aes(area = pop, fill = lifeExp, label = country, subgroup = continent)) +
  geom_treemap() +
  geom_treemap_text(colour = "black", place = "topleft", reflow = TRUE) +
  geom_treemap_subgroup_border() +
  geom_treemap_subgroup_text(
    place = "centre", grow = TRUE, alpha = 0.6, colour = "black",
    fontface = "italic", min.size = 0
    ) +
  scale_fill_gradient2(
    low  = "red", mid  = "white", high = "blue", midpoint = mean(df$lifeExp)
    ) +
  theme(aspect.ratio = 1/2)

2.2.1

library(conflicted)
library(tidyverse)
library(patchwork)

#
week <- c("", "", "", "", "", "", "")
data <- data.frame(
  week = factor(week, levels = week),
  sales = c(30, 25, 35, 28, 22, 34, 35),
  card_member = c(20, 13, 20, 14, 14, 20, 25),
  non_member = c(10, 12, 15, 14, 8, 14, 10)
)

#
p1 <- data |>
  ggplot(aes(x = week, y = sales)) + 
  geom_col(fill = "blue") + 
  theme(axis.title.x = element_blank(), legend.position = "none") +
  labs(title = "",  x= "", y = " []")

#
data_long <- data |>
  select(!sales) |>
  pivot_longer(!week, names_to = "membership", values_to = "sales")

p2 <- data_long |>
  ggplot(aes(x=week, y=sales, fill=membership)) +
  geom_col(position = "stack") + 
  theme(
    axis.title.x = element_blank(),
    legend.position = "none"
    ) +
  labs(y = " []", title = "")

#
p3 <- data_long |>
  ggplot(aes(x=week, y=sales, fill=membership)) +
  geom_col(position = "dodge") + 
  coord_flip() + 
  theme(legend.title = element_blank()) +
  labs(y = " []", x = "", title = "") +
  scale_fill_hue(name = "", labels = c(card_member = "", non_member ="") )

#
(p1 + p2) / p3

library(conflicted)
library(tidyverse)
library(patchwork)

week <- c("", "", "", "", "", "", "")
set.seed(0)
data.frame(
   = factor(week, levels = week),
  A = rnorm(7, 36, 0.2),
  B = rnorm(7, 36, 0.2)
  ) |>
  pivot_longer(!) |>
  ggplot(aes(x=, y = value, group = name, color = name, linetype = name, shape = name)) + 
  geom_line() +
  geom_point() + 
  theme(
    legend.title = element_blank()
    ) +
    labs(y = "[]", title="") + 
  theme(aspect.ratio = 1/2)

library(conflicted)
library(tidyverse)
library(patchwork)

people <- LETTERS[1:7]
set.seed(0)
df <- data.frame(
   = c(people, people),
  temp = rnorm(14, mean = 36.0, sd = 0.2),
  time_of_day = c(rep("", 7), rep("", 7))
  )

# 
p1 <- df |>
  ggplot(aes(
    x = , y = temp, group = time_of_day, shape = time_of_day,
    color = time_of_day, linetype = time_of_day)) +
  geom_point() +
  labs(title = "", x = "", y = " []" ) +
  theme(
    aspect.ratio = 1,
    legend.title = element_blank()
    )

p2 <- p1 +
  geom_line() +
  labs(title = "")

p1 + p2

library(conflicted)
library(tidyverse)
library(patchwork)

p1 <- data.frame(
  x = c("1","2"),
  avg = c(100, 80)
  ) |>
  ggplot(aes(x = x, y = avg)) +
  geom_col(fill = c("blue","orange")) +
  theme(axis.title.x = element_blank()) +
  labs(y = "", title = "") +
  coord_cartesian(ylim = c(0, 130))

# 
n_small <- 30
n_large <- 4
set.seed(0)
df_small_var <- bind_rows(
  data.frame(
     = rep("1", n_small),
     = rnorm(n_small, 100, 5) # 100530
    ), 
  data.frame(
     = rep("2", n_small),
     = rnorm(n_small, 80, 5) # 80530
    )
  ) 

p2 <- df_small_var |>
  ggplot(aes(x=, y=, color = )) + 
  geom_jitter(width = 0.1, height = 0) +
  theme(
    axis.title.x = element_blank(),
    legend.position = "none"
    )+
  labs(title = "\n") +
  coord_cartesian(ylim = c(0, 130))

set.seed(1)
df_large_var <- bind_rows(
  data.frame(
     = rep("1", n_large),
     = rnorm(n_large, 100, 20) # 100204
  ),
  data.frame(
     = rep("2", n_large),
     = rnorm(n_large, 80, 20) # 80204
  )
)

p3 <- df_large_var |>
  ggplot(aes(x=, y=, color = )) + 
  geom_jitter(width = 0.1, height = 0) +
  theme(
    axis.title.x = element_blank(),
    legend.position = "none"
  )+
  labs(title = "\n") +
  coord_cartesian(ylim = c(0, 130))

p1 + p2 + p3

library(conflicted)
library(tidyverse)
library(ggbeeswarm)
library(Hmisc)
library(patchwork)

num_samples <- 100 # 
set.seed(0)
data <- data.frame(
  Value = c(
    rnorm(num_samples, 100, 10), # 10010
    rnorm(num_samples, 80, 20)   # 8020
    ),
  Category = c(
    rep("3", num_samples), 
    rep("4", num_samples)
    )
  )

# ggplot2
plt <- data |>
  ggplot(aes(x=Category, y=Value)) +
  theme(
    axis.title.x = element_blank(),
    axis.title.y = element_blank(),
    legend.position = "none"
  )

#  (Dodge position)
p1 <- plt +
  geom_jitter(aes(color = Category), height = 0, width = 0.1)+
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0, 140)) +
  labs(title = "")

# 
p2 <- plt +
  geom_beeswarm(aes(color = Category),cex = 3) +
  labs(title = "")

# 
p3 <- data |>
  ggplot(aes(y=Value, fill=Category)) +
  geom_histogram(alpha=0.5, position='identity') +
  labs(title = "") +
  theme(
    axis.title.x = element_blank(),
    axis.title.y = element_blank(),
    legend.title = element_blank()
  )

# 
p4 <- plt + 
  geom_violin(aes(fill = Category),trim=FALSE) +
  geom_boxplot(width = .1, fill = "gray", color="black")+
  stat_summary(fun = mean, geom = "point", 
               shape =16, size = 2, color = "red", alpha = 0.5)+
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0, 140))+
  labs(title = "")

# 
p5 <- plt +
  stat_summary(aes(fill = Category),fun = "mean", geom = "bar") +
  stat_summary(geom = "errorbar",
               fun.data = "mean_sdl",
               width = 0.1, color = "black") +
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0, 140))+
  labs(title = "")

# 
p6 <- plt +
  geom_boxplot(aes(fill = Category)) +
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0, 140))+
  labs(title = "")

(p1 + p2 + p3) / (p4 + p5 + p6)

  Value = rnorm(100, mean=80, sd=20),
  Category = "4"
  ) |>
  ggplot(aes(x=Category, y=Value)) +
  geom_boxplot(fill = "orange", width = 0.5) +
  geom_beeswarm(shape = 21, cex = 3, fill = "orange", alpha=0.6) +
  coord_cartesian(ylim = c(0,140)) +
  labs(title = "") +
  theme(
    legend.position="none", 
    axis.title.x=element_blank(),

    )
